<L>__{interior upstairs bedroom}
<A>__{grady, laboring badly on his ankle", enters and finds a duffel bag open on the floor, its contents a tangle of quickly packed clothes. everything else in the room feels of another time. photographs are everywhere, documenting a pretty girl's life, from first recital to cap and gown. one photograph lies face down. grady turns it over and finds the pretty girl grown into a beautiful young woman, standing in a white gown next to a younger grady on their wedding day.}
